songs.title: Universe*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from snippet:

Beat 'em to death like No I.D
Streets full of envy, wanna kill me
'Cause I made a lot of money and I'm still me
Now the dollar bill don't thrill me
Know somebody feel me
Not Logic, but the real me
Under the surface I'm rhymin' with purpose
I know I ain't perfect, I'm Kirk and you irking me
All these go-getters ain't what they assert to be
I am the universe, you Captain Kirk to me
Nothing but regurgitating, far from innovative
I made it, I'm hated, I'm feelin' elated
Man, fuck who the greatest
Soon as I drop it, they play it
